highlights.text: Gang wale munde by Paradox is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 30 spots at #62.
AP Dhillon has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. Summer High is the highest at #5.
Chann Sitare (From "Oye Makhna") by Ammy Virk, Avvy Sra, and Harmanjeet Singh is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #44.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 57 weeks straight.
